{"tid":2233805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[切脂]美資投資顧問公司萬里富　關閉香港實體營運　表明與國安法有關","createTime":"2020-10-07T11:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T12:23:52.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20dd51279fb4705db93c93c45dfb9c6db14b6601","tid":2233805,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E8%B3%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%90%AC%E9%87%8C%E5%AF%8C-%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A6%E9%AB%94%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B-%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%88%87%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25AF%258C-%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258B-%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmb6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=4b1bb2ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25AF%258C-%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258B-%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C%2F&h=d7a8e6f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E8%B3%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%90%AC%E9%87%8C%E5%AF%8C-%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A6%E9%AB%94%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B-%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%88%87%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C/</a><br />\n<br />\n國安法生效後外資撤離香港再添一例。美資投資顧問公司萬里富 The Motley Fool 香港首席分析師向香港會員發信，指經歷去年反修例示威，近日北京推出香港國安法，加上中美脫鈎趨勢，令香港這個金融中心「處於地緣政治風暴的風眼中」，由於這些不確定因素，認為難以為未來 3 到 5 年在香港的業務發展作可預測決策，所以在權衡業務發展和員工後，決定關閉在香港的實體營運。<br />\n<br />\n萬里富香港首席分析師 Hayes Chan 10 月 5 日在公司網站發信予會員，指他們在約兩年前進入香港，傳統上大多數在香港經營的外國公司，都是希望利用香港自由資本流動、信息透明和西方法治來進入中國市場，但去年香港爆發反修例示威，令香港陷入曠日持久的政治危局，北京最近出台國安法，則令國際焦點重新聚焦於「一國兩制」模式及其未來前景，而中美脫鈎趨勢亦將令香港處於地緣政治風暴的風眼中。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">信件指由於這些不確定因素，他們難以作可預測決策，決定關閉香港實體營運，希望專注及投入資源到其他地方；Hayes Chan 又指，過去曾撰文分析香港投資者的投資組合，過份集中在香港和中國股票的風險，建議會員加入該公司在英、美、澳、加、日等的投資社區，令投資組合更多樣化。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"34a01c641dc2323c15f09afa3424b543535c9ede","tid":2233805,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />善意回覆 <br />\n睇下之後重有幾多走"},{"pid":"ba234667093b45ded727782a044e585f9116e6b5","tid":2233805,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"好撚多中產開曬離岸戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醒水就唔好擺咁多錢係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73dd55894fd4d7d73da0703f47c7ae1704f504d","tid":2233805,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"又話國安法令社會更加安定<br />\n點解d外資走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00b7a648f0ca061031edfd783a026dac116165f","tid":2233805,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"仆街 唉<br />\n佢地d文幾好睇<br />\n多d唔同方面意見<br />\n可以專心美股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1480352bee4c5766d1202d5ceebc569d45beaaa6","tid":2233805,"uid":168366,"li